data.description: Revel in the best of the best, featuring a new kitchen with exquisite quartz countertops and bathrooms boasting Jacuzzi tubs and smart toilets, especially in the master room. The AC, water heater, and ceramic tiles throughout the house are all brand new, ensuring modern comfort and style. Glass doors grace the bathrooms, while the pool system, complete with upgraded underground plumbing, promises a refreshing experience. Step outside onto the open patio porch and anticipate the upcoming installation of a brand new metal roof. The front showcases impact windows, while shutters grace the rear windows. Inside, discover upgraded window treatments, ceiling fans, and ceiling lights for a sophisticated ambiance. On the side, ample space for RVs and boats.
